Hello, thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Ralph Robinson. How may I assist you today?

Hi Ralph, I'm thinking about canceling my membership, but I’m feeling a bit unsure about it.

I understand, canceling your membership is a big decision. May I ask for your name so I can assist you better?

Of course, my name is Diana Griffin.

Thank you, Diana. To help you with the cancellation process, could I have your membership ID number?

Sure, my membership ID is zero nine eight seven six five.

Great, thank you. I also need to verify your email address on file. Could you please provide that for me?

Yes, it’s diana.griffin@email.com.

Thank you, Diana. I have all the information I need to guide you through the cancellation process. If you have any more questions or change your mind, feel free to reach out.

I appreciate your help, Ralph. I’ll make my decision soon.

You're welcome, Diana. Thank you for your time today. Have a great day!
